  "title": "Full Time Junior Chinese Teacher",
  "description": "<p>Are you familiar with the Singapore PSLE & O-Level syllabus? Do you want a career that combines teaching with curriculum innovation?</p><p>We are looking for educators to join us for the new academic year!</p><p><strong>💰 The Package:</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Salary:</strong> $2,600 - $3,200 / month</p></li><li><p><strong>Growth:</strong> Comprehensive On-the-Job Training (OJT) provided by Senior Teachers.</p></li><li><p><strong>Stability:</strong> 2-Year Contract (Renewable/Permanent).</p></li></ul><p><strong>📝 The Job Scope:</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Teach:</strong> Deliver engaging lessons for Primary & Secondary levels.</p></li><li><p><strong>Create:</strong> Assist in developing new curriculum materials.</p></li><li><p><strong>Manage:</strong> execute lesson plans (SOW) effectively and track student progress.</p></li></ul><p><strong>👤 Who We Are Looking For:</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Relevant Field:</strong> Diploma or Degree.</p></li><li><p><strong>Knowledge:</strong> Strong understanding of the local Chinese exam format (PSLE/O-Level).</p></li><li><p><strong>Vibe:</strong> You have an \"Educator's Heart\" patient, detail-oriented, and you genuinely enjoy working with kids and teens.</p></li><li><p><strong>Schedule:</strong> Able to work both weekends (when students are most active!).</p></li></ul>",
