    "uen": "202211205N",
    "description": "<p>SLC refers to School of Language and Communication and is founded in 2016 to promote Bilingual Education in English and Mandarin. Located conveniently outside Marymount MRT, we are a fast growing Language School specialising in online and offline English and Chinese tuition to prepare Primary and Secondary students for the PSLE, N and O level exams. Being a language specialist, we believe in professional development and continuous learning and improvement of our staff so as to provide high quality academic services to students and parents. We are also a believer in technology and blended learning where we are always exploring new ways to enhance our operations and learning.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>SLC was also featured in Today and CNA news: https://www.todayonline.com/big-read/big-read-short-tuition-craze-amid-pandemic</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We are looking for self motivated individuals who believe in this cause to join us and lets make all of this a greater success!</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>SLC，中文名称语文与传媒学院（语传院），建于2016年，为推动中英双语教育。坐落于玛丽蒙地铁站外，本公司是本地一家快速发展的语文学院，专为中小学生备考PSLE及N、O水准考试，提供线上及线下英文和华文补习课程。作为一所语文学院，我们致力于给团队战友们制定职业发展计划，鼓励团队不断学习新技能与寻求工作上的优化与改善，为了给学生及家长提供高质量的教学服务。我们也坚信科技及混合式学习的力量，不断探索尝试新方法，以加强学院的运作及各方学习效果。<br>\nSLC语传院接受过本地媒体今日报及亚洲电视台的采访（链接如上）。<br>\n倘您怀揣着一颗炙热的教育者之心，愿意与SLC共襄盛举，欢迎您与我们联系。</p>",
